<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" %>
<%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/include/taglib.jsp"%>
<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<meta name="decorator" content="help_center"/>
	<link href="${ctxStatic}/modules/front/css/help_center.css?${version }" rel="stylesheet"/>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<div id="content_bottom" class="help_content">
	
	<div class="help_main">
    	
        <div class="right_title"><span>项目投资</span></div>
    
    	<div class="content">
            <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
            
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>投标后能否申请取消？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>投资人一旦投标后，投标资金无法主动撤回。除非融资项目未满标前融资人主动撤回、借款审核失败或融资项目流标时，您的投标资金才会立刻退回您的账户。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>利息是什么时候起算的？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>为了合理平衡融资人和投资人的利益，投资利息是从融资项目投标截止日开始计算的。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse6" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>如何收回借款？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>融资人在规定的还款时间内通过花生金服将钱充值到易宝支付的个人账户中还款，系统会根据各位投资人的出借比例，自动将本息收益转入投资人的易宝支付个人账号，此金额实时在花生金服显示。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse7" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>投资后能不能提前收款？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>投资人成功投标后是无法申请提前收款的，除非融资人自愿提前还款。如果您投资的项目符合债权交易条件，您也可申请债权转让，提前变现。</p>
                    <p>债权交易链接：<a href="http://www.hsbank360.com" class="btn_text_gold">http://www.hsbank360.com/</a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse8" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>单笔投标有金额限制吗？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>参见每个项目的起投金额，在不超过融资总额情况下，投资无上限。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse9" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>是否可以提前收回出借的本金？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>您可以通过债权转让收回本金，有持有期限限制的项目，只有超过持有期限后才能转让。</p>
                    <p>相关阅读：<a href="" class="btn_text_gold">如何转出债权提前收回投资？</a><a href="" class="btn_text_gold">什么是债权转让？</a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse10" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>项目投资安全吗？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>为保障投资人的出借安全，花生金服设有适用于全体理财用户的<a href="" class="btn_text_gold">本金保障计划、以及严谨完善的风控体系</a>。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse12" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>投标前需要注意哪些事项？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse12" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>1.投标前认真阅读该笔借款的详细信息（包括借款金额、利息率、借款期限、借款者信用等级等），以确定您所要投的标的符合您的风险承受能力和所要求的投资回报率。</p>
                    <p>2.投标前请核实自己将要理财的金额，确认无误后再进行操作。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse13" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>如何投资项目？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse13" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>登录花生金服平台，点击【我要投资】--【项目列表】，选择借款标的，输入金额，点击【确认】完成投资。<a href="" class="btn_text_gold">查看操作流程>></a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse15" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>如何收取还款？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse15" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>融资人在规定的还款时间内将资金充值到与花生金服合作的第三方支付平台上，由第三方支付平台进行资金划拨操作进行还款，同时花生金服平台系统会发送短信以及邮件通知所有投资人融资人已成功还款。</p>
                    <p><span class="label label-important">注：</span> 融资人也可能提前偿还全部借款或者在到期日前手动提前偿还借款，请投资人注意查收花生金服发出的通知。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                  <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse16" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>融资人逾期怎么办？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                          </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse16" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                          <div class="panel-body">
                            <p>花生金服有一套完善的催收和多套处置机制，通过电话短信提醒、上门拜访、法律诉讼等多种方式，有效的监督了平台上融资人的及时还款。逾期还款的融资人需按约定交纳罚息。自逾期开始之后，正常利息停止计算。按照下面公式计算罚息：</p>
                            <p><Strong>逾期违约金=剩余金额*罚息利率*逾期天数，罚息利率为0.05%。</Strong></p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                          <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a data-toggle="collapse" onclick="collapseClick(this)" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse17" class="collapsed"><em class="icon_arrow_right"></em>融资人提前还款怎么办？<i class="icon_plus"></i></a>
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse17" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>融资人可以提前偿还借款，如果融资人提前偿还全部借款，除了当期本息外，需要额外支付给投资人剩余应还利息的30%作为违约金，融资人不需再支付后续的利息及管理费用。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
	function collapseClick(element) {
		if($(element).hasClass("collapsed")) {
			$(element).find("i").removeClass("icon_plus").addClass("icon_minus");
		}else {
			$(element).find("i").removeClass("icon_minus").addClass("icon_plus");
		}
	}
</script>
</body>
</html>
